</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-a6f9cf9f35eb47ceb6c160d75ce4b850" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>原创内容</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>翻译内容</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>个人资料</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>留言板</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>自检用</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>一些话</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1762">SCP-CN-1762——处女作</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>真的……回家了吗？</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1815">SCP-CN-1815</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>这只鸟看上去怪怪的。</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/never-back">再也回不去了</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>已是孤家寡人。</p>
</div>
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/transmigration">轮回</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>自嫌双泪下，不是解空人。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1844">SCP-CN-1844</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>“不知道真相对他们来说是一种残忍。”<br />
“但对于特定的人来说，沉浸在虚幻的乐土决非坏事。”</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none">
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4095">SCP-4095 爱你——翻译处女作</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>“简短，却又暖心。”</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4267">SCP-4267 烟道不通</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>一道烟囱，错综复杂的通道后藏着什么？</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4247">SCP-4247 普通的Bob</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>Bob不值得被人铭记。<sub>Bob很孤单。</sub></p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1674">SCP-1674 暗箱</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>简单的原理，造就的是身处异乡却无法回家的悲剧。</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1789">SCP-1789 愤怒的手指</a><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>此篇由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ora-spring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4400843); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4400843&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609510569" alt="Ora_Spring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4400843)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ora-spring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4400843); return false;">Ora_Spring</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-best-hunter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761736); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4761736&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609510569" alt="The best hunter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4761736)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-best-hunter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761736); return false;">The best hunter</a></span> 合译</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>待所谓主宰如同朝圣者。</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4268">SCP-4268 驱逐</a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sirens-sandbox-3/local--files/sirens-sandbox-2/folder.jpg) repeat; text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<p>失踪的人，会动的木雕，背后的真的仅是驱逐吗？</p>
</div>
<p><br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/old:scp-4456">SCP-4456——旧页面</a></p>
